    "description": "Grow your career with Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions! We are hiring a Guest Relations Manager for our Faridabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions:\nAnanda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Referral bonus program\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions!",
